{"tid":1033986,"cid":24,"subCid":0,"title":"【排隊黨亂日】Metal Build EVA初號機日本、香港開售　網民怒指中國排隊黨打尖、圍店員搶籌","createTime":"2019-02-23T14:43:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T15:25:48.000Z","uid":23993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dce6443d76a4dda3fdbbe3b56c4a97abfa848edd","tid":1033986,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:43:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/02/23/metalbuildeva/japan-gadget/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F02%2F23%2Fmetalbuildeva%2Fjapan-gadget%2Famp%2F&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1CDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=f7ba1b3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/02/23/metalbuildeva/japan-gadget/amp/</a><br />\n<br />\nMetal Build EVA 初號機今日同時在日本、香港等地發售。根據日本網民上傳社交媒體訊息，不少中國排隊黨獨佔龍頭位置，而且打尖情況嚴重。網民指保安勸喻排隊黨不要打尖時反被罵，雙方口舌之爭令場面混亂。其後部份中國排隊黨因拿不到籌圍繞店員抗議，更搶去店員手上的籌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/螢幕截圖-2019-02-23-下午5.44.31-1280x760.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2019-02-23-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%885.44.31-1280x760.png&h=5e63b8c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMetal Build EVA 初號機在日本、香港都引起熱潮。在香港 C3 展覽同時開售，每人限買一隻價格大約為 HK$1660，被秒殺後炒價已升到 HK$2,550，甚至有網路售價超過三千元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/螢幕截圖-2019-02-23-下午5.29.29-1280x785.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E6%88%AA%E5%9C%96-2019-02-23-%E4%B8%8B%E5%8D%885.29.29-1280x785.png&h=976f9723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲圖為香港C3展覽發售時Bandai攤位的狀況，現場消息指同樣有大陸人排隊，現場半小時售清存貨<br />\n<br />\n至於日本秋葉原售賣情況極為混亂。在 Twitter 上不少日本人指人龍的前面部份被疑似中國排隊黨佔領，周圍都聽到中國語。令網民更不滿的是不少疑似中國人插隊，警衛人員勸喻不要插隊卻反被罵，雙方繼而展開罵戰。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D0Dm49fVsAACrMc?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD0Dm49fVsAACrMc%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=6bb0857d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D0Dm49fUYAAgrVZ?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD0Dm49fUYAAgrVZ%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=25372d32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>SUNG<br />\n@sunggoh</em><br />\nメタルビルドのエヴァンゲリオン初号機一個も買えなかった\\( &circ;o&circ; )/<br />\n今回も転売ヤーの勝利だ&hellip;<br />\nバンダイさんよ、受注生産ってこんなに難しいの？<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/sunggoh/status/1099132233422499840\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsunggoh%2Fstatus%2F1099132233422499840&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1CDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=86465400\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsunggoh%2Fstatus%2F1099132233422499840&h=0999e4a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/sunggoh/status/1099132233422499840</a></blockquote><br />\n▲有網民指買不到初號機，卻見街頭不少排隊黨豐收，埋怨Bandai不能受注生產<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D0C0HZkUwAAw6Ti?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD0C0HZkUwAAw6Ti%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=3385b390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>Ayumi趣味垢！ホットトイズ！<br />\n@Ayumihottoys</em><br />\nこいつら軍団になってやりたい放題<br />\nいい加減にしてくれ<br />\n#転売ヤー #中華<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Ayumihottoys/status/1099076354870370305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAyumihottoys%2Fstatus%2F1099076354870370305&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1CDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=07e589f3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAyumihottoys%2Fstatus%2F1099076354870370305&h=44905a21\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Ayumihottoys/status/1099076354870370305</a></blockquote><br />\n▲網民指場面被「軍團」控制，「夠了吧」<br />\n<br />\n更混亂的是到了拿籌的時候，店員需要排隊人士講出商品名稱，才能分發籌券，但部份講不出商品名稱的疑似中國人不明白為何不被發籌，部份疑似集團排隊黨圍繞店員，大聲恐嚇店員，甚至搶去店員手上的籌。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D0DFG2GVAAAGVgz?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD0DFG2GVAAAGVgz%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=e8b3f3db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D0DFG2CU8AAKzHF?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD0DFG2CU8AAKzHF%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=531cb135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>まっさん<br />\n@rinosamansa</em><br />\n本日発売のバンダイMETAL BUILD エヴァンゲリオン初号機を求めてヨドバシ秋葉原に並んだのだが、中国人転売ヤー集団に占拠され買えず。<br />\nお店側も正確に商品名言えなければ券を渡さないという対策を取ったものの、言えなくて渡されなかった中国人が逆ギレし、店員を取り囲み掴むなどひどく醜い状況。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/rinosamansa/status/1099095038892564480\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frinosamansa%2Fstatus%2F1099095038892564480&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1CDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=1a2b4ade\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frinosamansa%2Fstatus%2F1099095038892564480&h=967ed440\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/rinosamansa/status/1099095038892564480</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n亦有網民拍攝到大批貨被排隊黨買走，放滿一車貨車的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/52856760_340328696581765_1417181513660760064_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F52856760_340328696581765_1417181513660760064_n.jpg&h=0b7d8132&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/52692348_2234893206778647_7366073713860542464_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F52692348_2234893206778647_7366073713860542464_n.jpg&h=68610f78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/52887297_623626391382996_5881427652778131456_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F02%2F52887297_623626391382996_5881427652778131456_n.jpg&h=032b6679&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D0DzV-zVAAATVLZ?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD0DzV-zVAAATVLZ%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=481d9820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<em>ふわふわ。もっちり☆彡<br />\n@fuwa_motchi</em><br />\n路上のメタビルエヴァなんて氷山の一角だった&hellip;(　ﾟдﾟ)！<br />\nこれ、全部METAL BUILDエヴァンゲリオンやぞ&hellip;<br />\n100位はありそう&hellip;根こそぎ転売屋に狩られとるやん&hellip;<br />\n#METALBUILD #エヴァンゲリオン<br />\n#転売屋<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/fuwa_motchi/status/1099145874834243584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffuwa_motchi%2Fstatus%2F1099145874834243584&d=gMg1FBwAZA1XbJy1Uvmn1CDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=c6181376\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffuwa_motchi%2Fstatus%2F1099145874834243584&h=1dd17581\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/fuwa_motchi/status/1099145874834243584</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"48853675394c42764f2e6ce2135a0b0cd9c65f30","tid":1033986,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:45:32.000Z","msg":"今日開賣 搞到一片混亂嘅點止得香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名等睇初號機變蟹貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59bded88e281c9d830da87736190d5fe5c377fde","tid":1033986,"uid":75582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:47:40.000Z","msg":"口中說不 蝗體卻很誠實"},{"pid":"8412b2d9386c0ae6a2a91f535d69989c5a99199d","tid":1033986,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48853675394c42764f2e6ce2135a0b0cd9c65f30","tid":1033986,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T14:45:32.000Z","msg":"今日開賣 搞到一片混亂嘅點止得香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hah